subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Lorena Ochoa shot a four-under 68 to take a one-shot lead over Jee Young Lee and Angela Stanford after the third round of the Safeway International in Superstition Mountain, Ariz. Ochoa moved into position for her second win in three starts this year.
